title: 135: The ALDI Haul Episode (February ‘21 Edition!)
itunes:title: The ALDI Haul Episode (February ‘21 Edition!)
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa and the gang try 14 food finds from ALDI! Stuff like sous vide egg bites, street corn dip, dessert hummus, sweet Hawaiian flatbread, cauliflower tortilla chips, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus the find of the episode, a hummus dip that’s perfectly called “Significantly Spicy,” and it’s SOOOO GOOD! Don’t waste another second! Push play now. Then head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of finds mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: Get ready for our biggest ALDI HAUL EVER!
